      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "诶？老师今天很忙吗 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:10",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "一直没回信息",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:10",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "是不是生气了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:11",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我生什么气？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:11",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh我没回信息的时候你不是也这么说我？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:11",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "好一个师夷长技以制夷",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:11",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我今天出差了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:12",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "长途飞行太累了 没看手机",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:12",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "啊啊啊啊  你去哪里出差了要长途飞行",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:12",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "来伦敦 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:13",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "啊你落地了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:13",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "(我讲什么废话呢，没落地怎么发信息）",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:13",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【擦汗】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:14",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "啊 我该不该说呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:14",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "其实我坐的航空有飞行wifi",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:14",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那我真是失敬了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:15",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "没做过国际航班 我很抱歉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:15",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "没事  你总会去的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:15",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "真的那么累吗 你连安慰我都很敷衍",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:16",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh真的很累啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:16",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我坐的是廉航 一路上腿都打不直",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:16",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "廉航怎么了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:17",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我就是坐廉航的  我骄傲",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:17",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你说的对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:17",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "重要的是能达到目的地",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:18",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那我撤回对助理的脾气",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:18",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你对助理发脾气了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:18",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么说?",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:19",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "也不是说发脾气吧 我批评了她",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:19",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "她是新人 刚来的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:19",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "出于想给公司开源节流 省钱的目的 特地给我订了廉航",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:20",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "但是她没有考虑过 我的飞行过程很疲惫 导致我见到投资人状态不好  错失了一些机会的话这将是更大的损失",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:20",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "...怎么说呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:20",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "职场新人是很...的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:21",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我刚入职场时也会这样 有时小心翼翼有时又想故作聪明来证明自己",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:21",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "对！就是故作聪明",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:21",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我有点哭笑不得",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:22",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不过你放心",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:22",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我也考虑到了她是新人 没有太过苛责",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:22",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【笑一笑算了】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:23",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【中国好老板】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:23",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你的赞美我收到了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:23",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "但我真的要去休息会了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:24",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【乖巧】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "23:24",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯嗯 去酒店吗？",
