      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:26",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "刚想发给你呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "今天 不见新的投资人了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我被鸽了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:27",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【苦笑】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【怎会如此】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那你直接回国吗还是？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:28",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "来都来了 我打算先逛逛",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "来都来了果然是中国人一生的态度",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh是啊 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:29",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我要是就这么直接回去了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我担心助理为了加倍的节省成本 直接让我坐火车回去",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【苦笑】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:30",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "教授不该是这个展开啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "按照小说 一个傻乎乎的新人助理应该得到霸总的青睐",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:31",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "你说的是小时代吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "牛的老师你怎么知道我在内涵小时代",
