      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "小时代不必内涵吧 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:32",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "明涵即可",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "作为一个标准的文青 你没和我羞辱过郭小四实在太不标准了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【笑cry】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:33",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那现在diss也不晚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "不过现在也过了当年那个群嘲的时代了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯？反而有种觉得也是青春的一部分的释怀吗？",
