      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:34",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh可以这么说吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "骂不骂的都已经过去那么久了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "成长使人宽容",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:35",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我好像没和你说过",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我是县城长大的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我就是在他的书里对大城市有了向往",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "没有地铁 遍地高楼 处处繁华",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:37",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "我也会穿上名牌出入办公楼这样",
