      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "那是因为我真的上了班！！！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "【小狗发火】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:38",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh那真的很坏了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
      "content": "其实我没怎么看过郭敬明",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾",
      "timestamp": "11:39",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": false
    },
    {
