    },
    {
      "content": "嗯嗯怎么了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "难道你遇到了艾琳？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你怎么老想着性缘关系？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "老天奶 我无辜啊 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我就说了一下下 怎么变成了老想着",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我的新助理你不也...",
