      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我确实对这种现象好奇",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么会第一时间转嫁到性缘关系呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你去问社会学家吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "别问我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我只是一个普普通通的公务员",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "又生气了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "陆清禾"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
